It seems that the [Scala ClassLoader doesn&#39;t play nicely with a Java classloader](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/7671888/scala-classloaders-confusion). I attempted to add a [URLClassLoader](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/net/URLClassLoader.html) as per another [SO post on setting a different classloader](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/17724481/set-classloader-different-directory) but the ClassNotFoundException continues.

