ERC20 token amount:  40000000000000000000
ERC20 token contract:  0x54a7cee7B02976ACE1bdd4aFad87273251Ed34Cf
ERC721 token ID:  12013
ERC721 token contract:  0x41cB4a771FdD019ADBF4685bd4885fbBeedE1784
```


